OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FExtreme weather events in the Channel
OL,7,FIslands will become more likely due to
OL,8,FClimate Change, according to a UK
OL,9,Fscientist.
OL,11,FMike Kendon is the lead author for the
OL,12,FUK Met Office's report into the state
OL,13,Fof Britain's climate.
OL,15,FHe says: "Our observations are telling
OL,16,Fus that our climate is changing right
OL,17,Fnow.
