OL,6,FHigh temperatures are not the only
OL,7,Fextreme weather events caused by
OL,8,FClimate Change with the Channel
OL,9,FIslands also facing bad flooding and
OL,10,Fmore aggressive storms.
OL,12,FThe Howard Davis Weather Station
OL,13,Freported 2023 as Jersey's wettest ever
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FStorm Ciaran brought hailstones the
OL,17,Fsize of ice lollies and a tornado to
OL,18,FJersey in November 2023, leaving
OL,19,Fresidents displaced and some homes
OL,20,Fbadly damaged.
