OL,3,CClimate scientist sheds light on
OL,4,Cextreme weather as report released
OL,6,FIt reached wind speeds of up to 186mph
OL,7,Fand is believed to have been the
OL,8,Flargest tornado to hit the British
OL,9,FIsles since 1954.
OL,11,FThe storm also led to violent sea
OL,12,Fswells and gale-force winds in
OL,13,FGuernsey where more buildings were
OL,14,Fdamaged and hundreds of trees fell.
OL,16,FA few months prior in Jersey, flash
OL,17,Fflooding hit the Grands Vaux area and
OL,18,F22 homes were left uninhabitable due
OL,19,Fto the heavy rainfall.
